# 📩 Jacameno Messaging App

A modern, real-time messaging application built with **Next.js**, **TypeScript**, and **Tailwind CSS**.  
Designed for speed, scalability, and a clean user experience — whether for personal use, team collaboration, or as a foundation for future chat-based projects.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 **User Authentication** (NextAuth.js / Firebase Auth)
- 💬 **Real-time Messaging** with WebSockets / Socket.IO
- 📱 **Responsive UI** powered by Tailwind CSS
- 🌓 **Dark/Light Mode** support
- 🗂️ Organized project structure using `src/` directory
- ✅ Code linting with ESLint + Prettier
- ⚡ Built with Next.js App Router for modern routing and layouts

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** Next.js (App Router), React, TypeScript  
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS  
- **Backend:** Next.js API Routes / Node.js  
- **Database:** PostgreSQL (via Prisma) or Firebase Firestore  
- **Real-time:** Socket.IO / WebSockets  
- **Auth:** NextAuth.js / Firebase Auth  

---

## 📂 Project Structure

jacameno-messaging-app/ │── public/ # Static assets │── src/ │ ├── app/ # Next.js App Router pages & layouts │ ├── components/ # Reusable UI components │ ├── lib/ # Config, helpers, utilities │ ├── styles/ # Global styles │ └── api/ # API routes (chat, auth, etc.) │── .eslintrc.json # ESLint config │── tailwind.config.js │── tsconfig.json │── package.json │── README.md

Code

